title: NextGenTel Holding AS: Acquisition of Kvantel Companies Completed
text:
NextGenTel Holding AS: Acquisition of Kvantel Companies Completed October 09, 2015 03:14 AM Eastern Daylight Time 
OSLO, Norway--( BUSINESS WIRE )--NextGenTel Holding ASA (OSE:NGT) 
Reference is made to a stock exchange notice issued on 17 September 2015 regarding the acquisition of Kvantel AS and Kvantel Voice AS. The acquisition of both companies has been completed on 8 October 2015. NextGenTel Holding ASA will invite to an investor and analyst meeting related to the acquisition. 
This information was brought to you by Cision http://news.cision.com Contacts
